profession.name: Scholar
profession.description: Scholars locate and research relics of ancient lore, relying on a vast knowledge of the world to produce scrolls and potions that aid in combat or craft.

profession.name: Metalsmith
profession.description: Metalsmiths use ingots of bronze, iron, and steel to forge shields and heavy-weight armour.

profession.name: Jeweller
profession.description: Jewellers create beautiful rings, necklaces, bracelets, and earrings from precious metals and valuable gemstones.

profession.name: Tailor
profession.description: Tailors use bolts of cloth and treated leather to create versatile lightweight and rugged medium-weight armour.

profession.name: Weaponsmith
profession.description: Weaponsmiths are skilled in both blacksmithing and bladecraft, combining these talents to produce fine metal weapons like swords and daggers.

profession.name: Woodworker
profession.description: Woodworkers shape and cut wood to produce hand-carved weapons like bows and staves.

profession.name: Cook
profession.description: Cooks use fresh produce and other ingredients to make a large variety of meals, snacks, soups, and strong drink.

profession.name: Farmer
profession.description: Farmers grow and harvest many types of crops including flowers, fruits, grains, pipe-weed, and vegetables.

profession.name: Forester
profession.description: Foresters locate and gather workable wood, producing treated timber for woodworkers. They have also mastered the skills of tanning, processing raw animal hides into leather for tailors.

profession.name: Prospector
profession.description: Prospectors locate and mine mineral deposits, smelt raw metal ore into ingots, and refine metals used by smiths and jewellers.

vocation.name: Armourer
vocation.description: An Armourer knows that all that stands between a good soul and the grave is often a thin sheet of metal.

vocation.name: Explorer
vocation.description: These canny travellers know much of the lands of Middle-Earth and its resources.

vocation.name: Armsman
vocation.description: An Armsman knows the many secrets of weaponry, and can craft almost any weapon imaginable.

vocation.name: Tinker
vocation.description: Fascinated by things intricate and beautiful, the Tinker seeks to create great things.

vocation.name: Yeoman
vocation.description: Hard-working and knowledgeable about the land, a Yeoman is well versed in farming, cooking, and tailoring.

vocation.name: Woodsman
vocation.description: A Woodsman is trained to survive off the land, and make weapons from natural materials.

vocation.name: Historian
vocation.description: Historians are the caretakers of lore and legend that the forces of light dare not forget.
